Set 1

Touch Of Gray-> Beat It On Down The Line, Loose Lucy, Little Red Rooster, Childhood's End, Dire Wolf, Black Throated Wind*, Bird Song

Set 2

Box Of Rain, Shakedown Street, Cassidy-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Drums-> Space-> The Wheel-> All Along The Watchtower-> Attics Of My Life-> Around & Around, E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text:
- I didn't see a lot of shows in 94: two, in fact: the June Seattle shows. The first night was the worst Dead show I'd ever heard. The second was the best I'd ever been to. I'm listening to this recent upload of this show today, and we'll see which side of the divide they fell on this night.

And it's pretty much right down the middle, which might have been a good show to go and hang wit people at, but not much good for listening to.
